{\an1}No one else made it.

222
00:13:57,084 --> 00:13:58,952
Take away all
of the corpses.

223
00:13:59,619 --> 00:14:02,923
{\an1}I mean every single one.
Search the buildings, too!

224
00:14:03,424 --> 00:14:04,724
{\an1}Who do you think could
have done something

225
00:14:04,758 --> 00:14:07,160
