Itachi Uchiha.

227
00:14:09,696 --> 00:14:10,630
Itachi?!

228
00:14:10,931 --> 00:14:13,100
{\an1}Itachi Uchiha harbored
a secret about his

229
00:14:13,134 --> 00:14:14,701
{\an1}clan: he despised it.

230
00:14:15,303 --> 00:14:18,139
{\an1}That is why he killed Shisui
and took his eyes for his

231
00:14:18,172 --> 00:14:21,242
{\an1}own, and also why
he caused infighting

232
00:14:21,275 --> 00:14:22,809
{\an1}among his brethren.

233
00:14:22,843 --> 00:14:24,245
{\an1}And in the end...

234
00:14:24,678 --> 00:14:26,781
{\an1}He committed this atrocity.

235
00:14:27,315 --> 00:14:29,150
{\an1}But why would he?

236
